    Convert atmospheric to sea level pressure

    Source: R/climatefunctions.R
    atmos_to_sea_pressure.Rd

    Convert atmospheric to sea level pressure

    Usage

    atmos_to_sea_pressure(pres, dtm)

    Arguments

    pres

    • vector or 3Darray or spatraster of atmospheric pressure - if array expects formatx,y,time

    dtm

    • vector or matrix or spatraster of elevations - if matrix or spatraster expected to match pres

    Value

    numeric or spatraster of atmospheric pressures matching dtm

    Examples

    atmos_to_sea_pressure(ukcpinput$pres,ukcpinput$dtm)
